items.title: Converge Bio raises $25M, backed by Bessemer and execs from Meta, OpenAI, Wiz
items.summary: AI drug discovery startup Converge Bio raised $25 million in a Series A . Bessemer Venture Partners, Meta, OpenAI, and Wiz are among the investors . The company is backed by the likes of Meta and Wiz, with additional backing from OpenAI and Wiz . It's the first time Converge has raised $50 million in its first round of funding .

items.title: NVIDIA Cosmos Reason 2 Brings Advanced Reasoning To Physical AI
items.summary: NVIDIA Cosmos Reason 2 Brings Advanced Reasoning To Physical AI . The new AI system is based on the work of NVIDIA's Cosmos AI AI . It is the first of its kind in the world of AI-powered virtual reality software . It will be the first attempt to use physical AI in the form of an AI-driven machine that works in the physical world .
